04:07.600 --> 04:10.000
葡英字典

04:13.600 --> 04:15.500
艾迪的老爹先生

04:17.900 --> 04:20.700
打得好
Hey! That's a great punch.

04:39.900 --> 04:41.100
饿肚子?

04:42.300 --> 04:43.800
饿肚子

04:59.100 --> 05:00.900
你要练习控制呼吸

05:01.700 --> 05:03.300
这里是掌控情绪

05:05.000 --> 05:09.000
恐惧是不好的 所以要控制情绪
Fear no good. So emotion and control.

05:12.500 --> 05:14.300
利用你的横膈膜

05:25.000 --> 05:27.400
想要控制你的怒气

05:28.200 --> 05:30.600
就要控制你的身体

05:31.700 --> 05:33.000
控制你的脉搏

05:33.100 --> 05:34.800
呼吸
Breathe.

05:38.000 --> 05:39.200
呼吸
Breathe.

05:43.100 --> 05:44.200
等一下
Wait.

06:55.000 --> 06:56.100
好
Okay.

07:01.100 --> 07:04.200
这只是暂时修好 你需要...
I can make it work for a while, but you need...

07:08.700 --> 07:11.100
我需要一间新工厂

07:11.200 --> 07:13.500
好 好
Okay. Okay.

07:14.100 --> 07:16.200
这五个月来你一直在帮我

07:16.600 --> 07:18.100
你太聪明 不该当临时工

07:18.900 --> 07:20.600
让我正式雇用你

07:30.100 --> 07:32.300
关掉!快关掉!
Shut that off! Turn it off!

07:36.000 --> 07:37.300
小心!
Watch out!

08:08.400 --> 08:09.500
好了
Okay!

08:40.900 --> 08:43.100
出口国- 美国

09:12.500 --> 09:14.000
你想跟我吃午饭吗?

09:15.800 --> 09:17.200
滚开 臭老外

09:23.400 --> 09:24.600
你想找麻烦吗?

09:25.100 --> 09:26.100
不想

09:26.200 --> 09:27.200
太迟了

09:28.100 --> 09:29.800
不要让我...饿肚子

09:30.600 --> 09:32.200
你不会喜欢我...

09:32.500 --> 09:33.900
饿肚子

09:35.300 --> 09:37.000
我用错字了
That's not right.

10:01.900 --> 10:03.100
太好了
Oh, you.

10:12.800 --> 10:16.400
看到没?看到吗? 我可以离开这鬼地方了
You see that? See that? My ticket out of here.

10:28.700 --> 10:31.900
加密中-呼叫蓝生生

10:32.000 --> 10:34.100
蓝 你在吗?

10:37.000 --> 10:38.300
绿先生 很高兴你打来

10:38.300 --> 10:40.600
蓝先生:我神秘的朋友 真高兴又跟你连络上!

10:42.200 --> 10:43.500
我找到了

10:44.000 --> 10:45.300
终于!

10:45.400 --> 10:47.600
那种花很美吧?

10:51.500 --> 10:54.600
务必要注射高剂量 祝好运

11:51.400 --> 11:52.600
可恶
Damn it!

11:53.600 --> 11:56.200
又一次失败

11:57.500 --> 11:59.400
你用了多少?

12:03.600 --> 12:05.700
全部

12:06.200 --> 12:08.400
我们该见面了

12:11.900 --> 12:13.400
不安全

12:14.200 --> 12:16.700
伽玛辐射感染很危险

12:16.800 --> 12:17.900
别再找花了

12:18.000 --> 12:19.900
寄血液样本给我

12:22.500 --> 12:24.500
要不然我就帮不了你

12:35.300 --> 12:36.900
绿先生

12:39.100 --> 12:40.900
蓝先生 纽约市

12:53.200 --> 12:55.400
维吉尼亚州阿灵顿

12:56.700 --> 12:57.900
这个你也许有兴趣
Here's something a bit more interesting.

12:58.100 --> 12:59.100
罗丝将军

12:59.200 --> 13:01.700
我们怀疑是伽玛中毒 密尔瓦基市
It's a possible gamma sickness. Milwaukee.

13:04.000 --> 13:06.800
有人喝了一瓶瓜拿纳果汽水
A man drank one of those guarana sodas.

13:07.700 --> 13:11.300
结果比他想像的更带劲
Guess it had a little more kick than he was looking for.

13:17.100 --> 13:20.000
- 汽水在哪里装瓶? - 波尔图港 巴西
- Where was it bottled? - Porto Verde, Brazil.

13:20.300 --> 13:23.900
派人到装瓶工厂找一个白人
Have our people look for a white man at the bottling plant.

13:24.100 --> 13:27.400
先按兵不动 要是被他看到他就会逃走
Tell them no contact! If he even sees them, he's gone!

13:28.600 --> 13:32.300
强生堡 佛州沼泽地

13:48.800 --> 13:51.600
我替你找到最顶尖的士兵
I got you who I could. Short notice, but they're all quality.

13:52.300 --> 13:53.700
其中有一个王牌
And I pulled you one ace.

13:58.800 --> 14:03.100
伊密布朗斯基 俄国出生 英国长大
Emil Blonsky. Born in Russia, raised in England.

14:03.600 --> 14:06.000
从皇家陆战队借调到特种部队
And on loan to SOCOM from the Royal Marines.

14:11.900 --> 14:14.300
我知道你动用了些人脉
I know you cashed in some chips for this, Joe.

14:14.400 --> 14:17.400
我很乐意帮忙 祝你任务成功
Glad I could help. Just make it good.

14:27.000 --> 14:30.600
这是目标和位置 这是逮捕行动 生擒活捉
This is the target and the location. Snatch and grab, live capture.

14:30.700 --> 14:32.600
你们要用麻醉枪
You'll have your dart clips and suppression ordnance,

14:32.700 --> 14:35.000
非不得已才能开枪
but live fire is for backup only.

14:35.100 --> 14:37.700
警方会协助 但不能打草惊蛇
We got local out there, but we want it tight and quiet.

14:37.800 --> 14:39.400
他会反抗吗?
Is he a fighter?

14:40.200 --> 14:43.800
目标是躲避美国政府的逃犯
Your target is a fugitive from the US government

14:43.900 --> 14:46.100
他窃取军事机密
who stole military secrets.

14:46.200 --> 14:50.800
也涉嫌杀害两名科学家
He is also implicated in the deaths of two scientists,

14:50.900 --> 14:54.700
一名军官一名爱达荷州州警 以及两名加拿大猎人
a military officer, an Idaho state trooper and possibly two Canadian hunters.

14:54.800 --> 14:57.900
所以别等他反抗
So don't wait to see if he's a fighter!

14:58.000 --> 15:00.800
把他麻醉然后带他回来
Tranq him and bring him back.

15:18.100 --> 15:21.100
有来电- 好消息

15:21.600 --> 15:24.600
初步验血显示伽玛量明显减少

15:30.800 --> 15:33.100
可以治好我吗?

15:33.600 --> 15:35.300
可以

15:39.900 --> 15:42.300
不过我需要更多资料

15:42.400 --> 15:43.900
拜托
Oh, come on.

15:44.300 --> 15:46.300
细胞感染程度- 伽玛浓度

15:49.400 --> 15:52.500
不可能- 资料不在这里

15:53.300 --> 15:54.900
在哪里?

16:05.700 --> 16:07.400
家里

16:47.100 --> 16:48.100
针孔摄影机
Camera.

16:50.800 --> 16:51.900
看到了
Here we go.

17:04.600 --> 17:06.100
把那只狗赶走
Get rid of the damn dog.

17:17.900 --> 17:19.000
抓住他!
Take him!

17:30.800 --> 17:32.600
目标在逃逸
Target's on the move.

17:41.300 --> 17:42.400
他在哪里?
Where is he?

17:48.700 --> 17:49.900
地面
He's on the ground.

17:50.100 --> 17:51.800
- 上吧! - 上吧!
- Let's go! - Go!

17:53.700 --> 17:54.700
快点!
Move, move!

17:57.500 --> 17:58.900
谢谢你

18:16.300 --> 18:17.900
快...快...
Go, go, go!

18:19.300 --> 18:20.800
开车!
Go! Go!

18:23.700 --> 18:25.500
把人群赶走
Clear everyone out!

18:26.700 --> 18:27.900
别追丢他
Do not lose him!

19:13.200 --> 19:15.000
哦 不
Oh! No!

20:26.700 --> 20:27.900
紧跟在他后面
Get around behind him!

20:29.400 --> 20:32.100
目标经过090机动车
Target moving past mobile unit 0-9-0.

20:46.700 --> 20:48.000
不是吧
Oh, no.

20:49.200 --> 20:51.200
别开玩笑
You got to be kidding me.

21:21.800 --> 21:24.000
- 他在哪里? - 看到目标
- Where is he? - Target acquired.

21:36.900 --> 21:38.000
臭老外
Gringo!

21:54.500 --> 21:55.600
一起滚!
Let's go.

22:09.200 --> 22:10.400
不
No!

22:11.200 --> 22:12.700
拜托 住手
Please! No!

22:15.000 --> 22:16.500
我的电脑
Not the computer!

22:16.800 --> 22:18.200
还给我
Gimme that! No!

22:24.300 --> 22:26.000
耍不了狠了吧?

22:26.300 --> 22:28.400
再来功夫那套呀

22:29.300 --> 22:30.400
请你住手

22:32.700 --> 22:34.100
当我...生气...

22:34.200 --> 22:35.200
会很坏

22:35.700 --> 22:39.700
你生气会很坏?我生气才会很坏
You bad angry, G? I very bad angry.

22:43.800 --> 22:44.800
噢 不
Oh, no.

22:46.100 --> 22:48.700
马上就会发生很糟的事
You don't understand! Something really bad is about to happen here!

22:49.900 --> 22:51.800
没错 你会遭殃

23:07.800 --> 23:09.800
有人看到吗?
Anybody else seeing this?

23:42.900 --> 23:44.800
有一个不明物体
We've got a bogey of some kind. Please advice.

23:44.900 --> 23:47.800
那就是目标 使用麻醉枪
That is the target! Use every tranq you've got!

23:48.100 --> 23:49.500
快点
Do it now!

23:57.100 --> 23:59.600
用真枪!用真枪!
Go live! Go live! Go live!

23:59.700 --> 24:01.500
- 走 - 离开这里!
- Move!- Get out of the way!

24:02.000 --> 24:03.200
不!
No!

24:35.800 --> 24:38.300
它在后面 快走
It's behind us! Move! Move!

24:46.900 --> 24:48.200
快开枪
Get him!

24:49.800 --> 24:51.000
开枪
Shoot!

25:05.800 --> 25:08.000
离...我...远点
Leave me alone.

26:19.200 --> 26:20.500
不!不!
No! No!

26:32.800 --> 26:35.400
开枪前我就知道事情不对
I knew something was different before I got the shot off.

26:35.500 --> 26:37.800
他逃走时留下这个
He had it on him when he bolted.

26:44.000 --> 26:47.300
这是他女友?她在帮他?
Is that a girlfriend? She helps him, maybe?

26:50.400 --> 26:53.200
她不再是个问题
She is no longer a factor.

26:53.300 --> 26:56.700
他们早就失联 他是一个人
We closed that door to him a long time ago. He's alone.

26:56.900 --> 27:00.900
他也想要离群索居 不过查查看他有和谁联络
He wants to be alone. But see if he's been talking to anybody.

27:08.700 --> 27:10.300
恕我冒昧
Forgive me, sir?

27:11.500 --> 27:14.800
没有人想谈谈刚才的事吗?
Doesn't anybody want to talk about what went down in there? 'Cause...

27:16.300 --> 27:17.600
不是他甩掉我们
He didn't lose us.

27:17.700 --> 27:21.500
他也不是一个人
And he was not alone, sir. We had him.

27:21.600 --> 27:23.900
我们把他困住了 只是后来被攻击
And then something hit us, something...

27:24.100 --> 27:26.900
一个很大的东西
Something big hit us!

27:28.900 --> 27:32.200
它把堆高机当作垒球丢
It threw a forklift truck like it was a softball!

27:34.200 --> 27:37.800
它是我见过力量最强大的东西
It was the most powerful thing I've ever seen.

27:38.700 --> 27:40.300
它不见了
Well, it's gone.

27:42.700 --> 27:44.300
要是班纳知道那是什么
Well, if Banner knows what it is,

27:44.400 --> 27:47.500
我会逮到他
I'm gonna track him down, I'm gonna put my foot on his throat

27:47.700 --> 27:49.500
- 逼他说出... - 那就是班纳
- and I'm gonna... - That was Banner.

27:54.300 --> 27:55.400
它...
It

27:57.100 --> 27:58.500
就是班纳
was Banner.

27:58.800 --> 28:02.800
- 你必须解释清楚 长官 - 我不必解释
- You have to explain that statement, sir. - No, I don't.

28:05.300 --> 28:07.000
你表现得很好
You've done a good job.

28:08.500 --> 28:12.500
收拾好就带队上飞机 我们要回家
Pack up and get our men on a plane. We're going home.

29:03.400 --> 29:05.600
距离上次变身-第1天

29:17.100 --> 29:18.300
停车
Wait.

29:20.900 --> 29:22.200
拜托
Please.

29:24.100 --> 29:25.400
你能帮忙吗?

29:25.700 --> 29:27.000
我不会说葡萄牙话

29:29.400 --> 29:30.800
我在哪里?
Where am I?

29:32.100 --> 29:33.300
我在哪里?

29:34.500 --> 29:36.200
瓜地马拉

29:36.800 --> 29:39.200
我要去下一个城镇

29:42.600 --> 29:43.700
你能帮我吗?

29:44.700 --> 29:46.100
上车

29:48.100 --> 29:49.300
来 披着

29:56.900 --> 29:58.100
你要去哪里?

29:58.500 --> 30:00.200
回家

30:06.400 --> 30:09.400
我以前出任务也出过差错
I've run into bad situations on crap missions before.

30:09.600 --> 30:10.600
同袍因为
I've seen good men go down

30:10.700 --> 30:14.000
事先不知情白白牺牲
purely because someone didn't let us know what we were walking into.

30:14.200 --> 30:16.400
但我是军人 必须继续战斗
I've moved on to the next one, because that's what we do, right?

30:16.600 --> 30:17.900
这是我们的天职
I mean, that's the job.

30:18.000 --> 30:19.200
但是这玩意?
But this?

30:21.200 --> 30:23.900
这件事太诡异了
This is a whole new level of weird.

30:24.000 --> 30:26.800
我不能就这样撒手不管
And I don't feel inclined to step away from it.

30:26.900 --> 30:30.000
如果你要再去抓他 我要参一脚
So if you're taking another crack at him, I want in.

30:30.100 --> 30:33.900
这次一定要事先准备好
And, with respect, you should be looking for a team that's prepped and ready to fight,

30:34.000 --> 30:36.000
因为要是那玩意再出现
because if that thing shows up again,

30:37.200 --> 30:40.800
最勇敢的军人也会被吓得尿裤子
you're gonna have a lot of professional tough guys pissing in their pants.

30:41.800 --> 30:42.600
长官
Sir.

30:49.500 --> 30:52.100
墨西哥恰帕斯

31:33.100 --> 31:34.900
有没有更宽的裤子?
Tienes mas stretchy?

31:36.600 --> 31:39.000
很好
Yeah. Perfecto.

32:10.200 --> 32:12.500
我要告诉你的事非常敏感
Let me emphasise that what I'm about to share with you

32:12.600 --> 32:15.900
对我和对军方都一样
is tremendously sensitive, both to me personally and the Army.

32:18.800 --> 32:21.900
你应该知道美国的武器研发计划
You're aware that we've got an Infantry Weapons Development programme.

32:22.000 --> 32:26.700
二次大战期间 他们进行新实验
Well, in WWII, they initiated a subprogram

32:26.800 --> 32:29.300
生物科技力量增强实验
for Bio- Tech Force Enhancement.

32:29.400 --> 32:31.200
打造超级大兵
Yeah, Super Soldier.

32:33.700 --> 32:34.700
没错
Yes.

32:35.600 --> 32:37.800
没这么简单 但是没错
An oversimplification, but yes.

32:38.700 --> 32:42.600
我命令他们再度进行大胆实验
And I dusted it off, got 'em doing serious work again, bold work.

32:42.700 --> 32:45.400
研发部只想制造更好的武器
Across the hall, they were trying to arm you better.

32:45.500 --> 32:47.700
我们则想打造更强的士兵
We were tryin' to make you better.

32:51.100 --> 32:56.400
班纳的实验只达到初步阶段 根本就还不能应用
Banner's work was very early phase. It wasn't even weapons application.

32:56.600 --> 32:59.100
他以为他在研究抗辐射方法
He thought he was working on radiation resistance.

32:59.200 --> 33:02.400
我从来没告诉他真相
I would never have told him what the project really was.

33:02.500 --> 33:07.100
但他太有把握了 竟然私自进行人体实验
But he was so sure of what he was onto, that he tested it on himself.

33:07.200 --> 33:10.000
结果出了大错
And something went very wrong.

33:12.500 --> 33:14.300
或者是完全做对了
Or it went very right.

33:15.200 --> 33:19.200
他的身体是属于美国军方的
As far as I'm concerned, that man's whole body is the property of the US Army.

33:19.300 --> 33:22.300
你说他不是研发武器 对吧?
You said he wasn't working on weapons, right?

33:22.400 --> 33:24.500
- 是的 - 但你是 是你 对吧?
- No. - But you were. You were, weren't you?

33:24.600 --> 33:26.600
但是你们在进行别的实验
You were trying other things.

33:26.700 --> 33:29.600
我们研发出一种
One serum we developed

33:30.800 --> 33:32.100
很有潜力的血清
was very promising.

33:32.300 --> 33:34.800
- 他为什么要逃亡? - 他是个科学家
- So why did he run? - He's a scientist.

33:36.300 --> 33:38.100
不是军人
He is not one of us.

33:41.400 --> 33:45.400
- 你几岁?45岁? - 39岁
- Blonsky, how old are you? 45? - 39.

33:46.300 --> 33:49.900
- 打仗老得快 对吧? - 没错
- It takes a toll, doesn't it? - Yes, it does.

33:49.900 --> 33:51.200
那就别再出任务
So get out of the trenches.

33:51.300 --> 33:53.700
以你的记录 你可以当上校
You should be a Colonel by now, with your record.

33:53.900 --> 33:57.900
不 我是战士 永远都是
No, I'm a fighter. I'll be one for as long as I can.

33:58.200 --> 34:01.400
如果十年前的我有我现在的经验
You know, if I could take what I know now, put it in the body I had ten years ago,

34:01.500 --> 34:04.200
我绝对不会跟我自己对决
that would be someone I wouldn't want to fight.

34:06.100 --> 34:09.100
我可以让你变得更强
I could probably arrange something like that.

34:14.200 --> 34:16.300
维吉尼亚州卡尔弗大学

34:28.000 --> 34:29.400
距离上次变身-第17天

35:10.400 --> 35:12.900
生物科学系大楼

35:15.200 --> 35:19.700
伊莉莎白罗斯博士- 细胞生物学

36:25.700 --> 36:28.100
史丹利比萨餐馆

36:30.300 --> 36:32.000
保重了
Take care, kids.

36:32.600 --> 36:34.800
打烊

36:43.400 --> 36:44.700
史丹 我发誓
Stan, I give you my word,

36:44.900 --> 36:46.500
有关我的谣言都不是真的
whatever you've heard about me, it's not true.

36:46.600 --> 36:49.800
我知道 我一直都知道
Oh, I know it. I always knew it.

36:49.900 --> 36:52.600
你也知道我跟你们俩的交情
I mean, you know how I felt about you two.

36:55.600 --> 36:58.500
- 你去找过她吗? - 没有
- Have you talked to her? - No.

36:58.600 --> 37:00.800
她不知道我在这里
She doesn't know that I'm here.

37:02.600 --> 37:07.000
- 她有男友了? - 对 他是精神科医师
- She's with somebody? - Yeah, he's a head shrink.

37:07.100 --> 37:10.500
听说是最顶尖的 好人一个
They say he's one of the best. But a really nice guy.

37:13.600 --> 37:15.400
很好 那很好
Good. That's good.

37:15.500 --> 37:20.300
- 布鲁斯 我能帮你什么忙? - 我需要地方住几晚
- Bruce, what can I do to help you? - I could use a bed for a few nights.

37:20.400 --> 37:24.300
- 你可以用楼上的空房间 - 那真是太好了
- You can have the spare room upstairs. - That'd be so great.

37:26.100 --> 37:28.300
还有另一件事
There is one other thing.

37:32.400 --> 37:34.200
抱歉 不好意思
Excuse me. Pardon me.

37:35.800 --> 37:37.300
借过
Coming through.

37:41.900 --> 37:43.800
老兄 我要送比萨到五楼
Hey, pal. I got a delivery on five.

37:44.800 --> 37:46.200
五楼没人了
I don't think there's anybody up there.

37:46.300 --> 37:50.800
收不到钱我就惨了 拜托让我上去看看
Oh, man. I'm gonna catch hell if I don't collect. You got to let me try.

37:52.700 --> 37:56.300
我多了一块比萨 我请客
I'll tell you what. I got an extra medium. Take it on the house.

38:03.200 --> 38:06.300
- 你很上道 - 老天保佑你 兄弟
- You are the man. - God bless you, brother.

38:08.900 --> 38:10.000
好
All right.

38:52.300 --> 38:55.000
使用者帐号:罗斯博士

39:03.400 --> 39:06.500
密码

39:07.800 --> 39:08.800
好
Okay.

39:13.900 --> 39:17.300
计划名称:伽玛脉冲 搜寻中

39:19.700 --> 39:20.700
查无此资料

39:23.500 --> 39:25.500
搜寻参数- B.班纳

39:27.700 --> 39:29.500
查无此资料

39:37.300 --> 39:38.300
加密纲

39:38.400 --> 39:40.600
登入- 远端聊天

39:43.900 --> 39:46.000
加密中- 呼叫蓝先生

39:48.800 --> 39:51.400
绿先生 找到资料了吗?

39:51.500 --> 39:54.000
资料不见了

39:54.300 --> 39:56.500
没有资料...

39:56.600 --> 39:57.900
我帮不上忙

40:01.600 --> 40:03.400
现在怎么办?

40:03.700 --> 40:08.000
我必须继续逃亡

40:22.400 --> 40:24.800
我们打烊了 抱歉
We're pretty well closed here, folks. I'm sorry.

40:24.800 --> 40:27.300
拜托 史丹 周五夜耶
Oh, come on, Stan. It's Friday night.

40:28.400 --> 40:30.100
先说好
Oh, kids.

40:30.600 --> 40:32.800
除了意大利干酱什么都没了
I got nothing but marinara now.

40:32.900 --> 40:34.900
我一定要吃块比萨
Oh, I got to have a Mister Pink, please.

40:35.000 --> 40:37.200
她忙着工作 又没吃晚饭
She worked through dinner again, of course.

40:45.000 --> 40:46.100
史丹?
Stan?

40:47.500 --> 40:51.800
我说:"你在哪里?
And he... I go, "So, yeah, I mean, where were you?

40:52.000 --> 40:54.000
"我不知道你在哪里"
"I can't... I don't know where you were, Cecil."

40:54.000 --> 40:56.500
他说:"我没在你那里"
And he goes, "Not where you been at."

40:56.600 --> 41:00.300
我想 "噢 上帝啊" 感觉真是太糟了
I thought, "Oh, my God." I just felt so awful.

41:27.900 --> 41:29.300
布鲁斯?
Bruce?

41:35.900 --> 41:39.000
贝蒂?怎么了?
Betty? What's going on?

41:54.300 --> 41:55.400
贝蒂...
Betty...

41:55.500 --> 41:58.600
我看到的是不是真的?
Just tell me if I saw what I think I saw.

41:59.900 --> 42:03.600
- 我不知道该说什么 - 拜托你说实话
- I don't know what to say. - Please, just tell me the truth.

42:45.000 --> 42:47.600
别走 别走
Don't go. Don't go.

42:57.500 --> 42:59.400
我要你跟我来
I want you to come with me now.

42:59.500 --> 43:01.700
拜托 跟我来
Please. Come with me.

43:03.200 --> 43:04.400
求求你
Please.

43:34.500 --> 43:36.000
这是我们的资料
It's our data.

43:37.000 --> 43:40.000
我趁他们把一切搬走前拿的
I got in there before they carted it all away.

43:42.200 --> 43:45.900
希望有一天能找到解答
I hoped somewhere that it might tell us something someday.

43:48.300 --> 43:52.900
- 将军知道这件事吗? - 应该不知道
- Does the General know that you have this? - No, I don't think so.

43:53.000 --> 43:55.300
我有两年没跟他说话
I haven't spoken to him in a couple of years.

43:55.500 --> 43:56.900
你一定要确定
You have to be sure.

43:57.100 --> 44:02.100
为什么不能一起直接去找他?
Bruce, I don't understand why we can't just go in there together and talk to him.

44:02.100 --> 44:07.100
他跟我说过他想做什么 他要取出我体内的细胞
He told me what he wanted to do. He wants it out of me.

44:07.200 --> 44:10.400
进行分析后再复制它
He wants to dissect it so that he can replicate it.

44:10.600 --> 44:12.700
让它成为武器
He wants to make it a weapon.

44:33.100 --> 44:36.600
冷冻计划:增强武器

45:07.100 --> 45:11.000
- 我猜你会想要... - 谢了
- I thought you might want to... - Thanks.

45:12.900 --> 45:16.500
我最好早点走 愈早愈好
Listen, I should leave early, as early as I can.

45:16.500 --> 45:20.000
真的?你不能待下来?
Really? You can't stay at all?

45:20.100 --> 45:23.400
我很想 但是这里不安全
I want to, but it's just not safe for me to be here.

45:26.000 --> 45:28.700
- 我能借点钱吗? - 当然了
- If I could borrow some cash... - Of course.

45:28.800 --> 45:30.400
我得搭巴士
I need to take a bus.

45:30.500 --> 45:33.200
至少让我陪你去车站
Well, at least let me walk you to the station.

45:35.200 --> 45:36.300
好吧
Okay.

45:40.200 --> 45:42.600
- 该有的都有了吗? - 晚安
- You have everything you need? - Yeah.

45:45.800 --> 45:46.900
我
I...

45:48.300 --> 45:49.400
什么
What?

45:51.800 --> 45:53.800
晚安
- Good night. - Good night.

45:53.900 --> 45:55.900
尽量休息吧
I hope you get some rest.

46:38.000 --> 46:40.700
我们会替你注射最低剂量
We're giving you a very low dose only.

46:41.100 --> 46:43.700
我要你保持专注听命行事
I need you sharp out there and disciplined.

46:43.800 --> 46:45.800
只要出现副作用
First sign of any side effect,

46:45.900 --> 46:49.500
我就喊停 等你恢复以后才能复职
we stop and you're off team until you straighten out.

46:50.300 --> 46:52.100
- 同意吗? - 同意
- Agreed? - Agreed.

46:56.000 --> 46:58.700
你要打两次针
You'll get two separate infusions.

46:58.800 --> 47:02.800
一针打入深肌 一针打入骨髓
One into the deep muscle, one into the bone marrow centres.

47:03.200 --> 47:05.400
第二针会很痛
The bone ones are going to hurt.

47:52.000 --> 47:53.800
没事吧?
Is everything okay?

47:55.800 --> 47:57.100
应该没事
I think so.

48:05.600 --> 48:06.800
过来
Come here.

48:08.600 --> 48:10.600
我帮你拉出来
- I just wanna do this. - Oh.

48:11.800 --> 48:13.800
这样比较好看
- It's better like that. - Yeah?

48:18.600 --> 48:20.100
帽子太小了
It feels too tight, huh?

48:20.200 --> 48:22.000
是有点小
- Yeah, a little. - Okay.

48:29.500 --> 48:32.500
- 怎么了? - 他们来了
- What? - They're here.

48:32.800 --> 48:34.200
贝蒂 离我愈远愈好 快走
- Betty, look at me, look at me! - Bruce!

48:34.300 --> 48:35.500
你离我远点!
You have to go far away from me as you can!

48:35.700 --> 48:37.100
- 别和我争了 走就是了 快走!
- Don't argue with me, just go. Go!- Bruce!

48:48.300 --> 48:50.400
3分钟后狙击手就会到位
Damn it! We'd have had snipers on target in three more minutes.

48:50.500 --> 48:52.100
是谁擅自行动?
I wanna know who jumped the gun.

48:54.400 --> 48:55.500
他逃向270方位
He's heading 2- 7- 0.

49:12.700 --> 49:14.300
布朗斯基 还不行
Blonsky! Not yet!

49:15.800 --> 49:17.000
长官
Sir.

49:18.600 --> 49:20.200
注意看 这会很有趣
Look alive. This could get interesting.

50:08.300 --> 50:09.300
看到他了
I got him!

50:09.600 --> 50:12.700
停车!停车!
Stop! Stop!

50:14.500 --> 50:15.900
我知道你在里面
I know you're in there!

50:17.800 --> 50:19.400
将军 求求你
General, please!

50:21.900 --> 50:22.900
长官?
Sir?

50:23.500 --> 50:24.600
爸!
Dad!

50:32.100 --> 50:36.100
- 爸 求求你住手 - 你不清楚状况
- Dad, please don't do this. - You can't see this clearly. Now, get inside.

50:36.300 --> 50:38.100
他在那里!
There he is!

50:38.200 --> 50:40.400
目标在天桥
Target is in the overpass. We have a visual.

50:40.500 --> 50:42.700
不要进去
Do not engage! Repeat, do not engage!

50:48.400 --> 50:49.900
他被锁在里面
He's locked in.

50:56.000 --> 50:57.500
发射两枚催泪弹
Put two canisters in there with him.

50:58.100 --> 50:59.200
发射!
Fire!

51:18.300 --> 51:19.500
把她带回来
Get her back here!

51:54.000 --> 51:55.000
她会看清真相
Now she'll see.

52:17.900 --> 52:19.000
A队?
Alpha team?

52:21.100 --> 52:22.100
全力开火
Let him have all of it.

52:28.400 --> 52:29.900
来 干掉他!
Come on, light him up!

52:33.200 --> 52:36.400
50口径火炮呢?快上呀!
Where are the fifty cals? Move your asses!

53:24.600 --> 53:25.800
我的老天!
Oh, my God!

53:29.500 --> 53:30.500
布朗斯基 上吧
Blonsky, now you're up!

53:31.200 --> 53:32.300
长官
Sir?

53:33.500 --> 53:34.800
掩护我
Cover me.

53:52.900 --> 53:54.400
记得我吗?
Remember me?

54:14.400 --> 54:15.800
天啊 他真的变强了
My God, he's doing it.

54:20.800 --> 54:22.100
把他引到音波炮那里
Move him toward the cannons!

54:28.300 --> 54:29.400
启动!
Move!

54:42.900 --> 54:44.100
守好你的位置!
Hold your position!

54:44.200 --> 54:45.500
就现在
Do it now!

55:11.400 --> 55:12.900
求求你住手
Please, please, please, no!

55:13.100 --> 55:14.400
- 求你 - 让她回来
- Please, please, please!- Get her back!

55:14.600 --> 55:15.600
你会杀死他
You're killing him!

55:15.600 --> 55:18.000
住手!放开我!
Stop! Get off of me!

55:18.100 --> 55:19.500
布鲁斯!
Bruce!

55:22.600 --> 55:26.500
布鲁斯!
Bruce! Bruce!

55:55.900 --> 55:56.900
攻击直升机呢?
Where's the gunship?

56:17.100 --> 56:18.200
就这样?
Is that it?

56:18.400 --> 56:20.200
布朗斯基 撤退!
Blonsky, pull back now.

56:20.300 --> 56:21.500
回来
Pull back!

56:24.700 --> 56:26.500
你就只有这点料吗?
Is that all you got?

56:34.100 --> 56:36.600
- 撤退! - 撤退!
- Fall back! - Fall back! Let's go, let's go!

56:36.700 --> 56:38.100
快找掩护!
Find cover!

56:42.100 --> 56:43.300
贝蒂!
Betty!

56:56.800 --> 56:58.300
快开火呀!
Fire, goddamn it!

57:00.100 --> 57:01.300
布鲁斯?
Bruce?

57:14.500 --> 57:15.600
停火!
Stop firing!

57:29.200 --> 57:30.600
不!
No!

58:20.800 --> 58:23.300
你打给我是对的
You did the right thing, calling us.

58:25.500 --> 58:28.300
我要知道他们去哪里
I need to know where they're going.

58:28.500 --> 58:30.600
她跟他在一起很危险
She'll be in incredible danger as long as she's with him.

58:30.700 --> 58:32.000
谁会伤害她?
From who?

58:32.900 --> 58:35.500
他保护她 你却差点害死她
He protected her. You almost killed her.

58:35.600 --> 58:39.300
我保证 她的安危最重要
I give you my word, her safety is my main concern at this point.

58:39.400 --> 58:42.100
身为精神科医师的我
You know, it's a point of professional pride with me

58:42.200 --> 58:45.100
看得出谁说谎
that I can always tell when somebody's lying.

58:45.500 --> 58:46.500
你在说谎
And you are.

58:47.900 --> 58:50.100
我不知道他去哪里
I don't know where he's going.

58:51.100 --> 58:55.100
- 我只知道她一定会帮他 - 那她就算是协助逃犯
- I know she'll help him, if she can. - Then she's aiding a fugitive.

58:56.500 --> 58:59.000
我也帮不了他们
And I can't help either one of them.

59:04.100 --> 59:07.200
我一直在想她为什么从不提起你
I used to wonder why she never talked about you.

59:07.600 --> 59:09.000
现在我知道原因了
Now I know!

59:13.900 --> 59:16.200
她都在哪里率墩庑┭方
Where does she meet these guys?

01:00:05.700 --> 01:00:06.900
布鲁斯?
Bruce?

01:00:17.100 --> 01:00:18.200
布鲁斯
Bruce.

01:00:38.500 --> 01:00:40.600
没关系 没有事
It's okay. It's okay.

01:00:53.800 --> 01:00:56.500
过来 跟我来
Come here. Come this way.

01:00:59.700 --> 01:01:01.300
小心头
Watch your head.

01:01:28.400 --> 01:01:29.500
我们没事
We're okay.

01:01:34.500 --> 01:01:35.900
没事
It's okay.

01:01:37.700 --> 01:01:39.400
只是下雨而已
It's just the rain.

01:01:48.700 --> 01:01:50.800
他能再走路吗?
Will he ever walk again?

01:01:51.000 --> 01:01:54.500
他全身的骨头支离破碎
Most of the bones in his body look like crushed gravel right now.

01:01:54.600 --> 01:01:58.400
不过我很佩服他 他的心脏像个机器
I will say this for him. He's got a heart like a machine.

01:01:58.500 --> 01:02:01.700
就跟赛马一样强
Never seen anything like it, outside of a racehorse.

01:03:04.300 --> 01:03:05.400
来
Here.

01:03:48.800 --> 01:03:50.000
布鲁斯?
Bruce?

01:03:53.300 --> 01:03:54.400
你还好吧?
Are you okay?

01:03:55.100 --> 01:03:56.200
我好多了
Yeah.

01:03:56.400 --> 01:03:58.600
事实上 我感觉好多了
Yeah, actually, I feel a lot better.

01:03:58.800 --> 01:04:01.300
- 那就好 - 我得把资料拿出来
- Good. - I just had to get my data back.

01:04:02.900 --> 01:04:04.000
你把它吃掉?
You ate it?

01:04:04.100 --> 01:04:08.100
情况紧急 我总得想办法
Well, you know, the circumstances called for a little improvisation.

01:04:11.000 --> 01:04:15.300
款式不多 不过你有一些选择
Okay, so they didn't have a great selection, but I got you some options.

01:04:15.400 --> 01:04:18.000
这玩意比较重要
First thing's first.

01:04:18.100 --> 01:04:19.700
你在开玩笑吧?
Oh, you're kidding me.

01:04:30.000 --> 01:04:31.100
怎么了?
What?

01:04:31.700 --> 01:04:34.600
这是最宽松的一件
- No. - They were the stretchiest pair they had.

01:04:34.600 --> 01:04:35.900
我宁愿冒险
I'll take my chances.

01:04:36.200 --> 01:04:38.600
有关于军队和不明敌人
Rumours continue to swirl about a violent clash

01:04:38.800 --> 01:04:42.600
在卡尔弗大学校园发生激烈战斗的谣言
between forces of the US military and an unknown adversary

01:04:42.600 --> 01:04:45.600
持续延烧
on the campus of Culver University earlier today.

01:04:45.700 --> 01:04:48.900
两名大二学生目击整个事件
Sophomores Jack McGhee and Jim Wilson witnessed some of the battle.

01:04:49.000 --> 01:04:50.500
那玩意超大的
It was so big.

01:04:50.600 --> 01:04:53.400
就像一个绿色巨人
- It was like this huge, like, hulk! - Yeah.

01:04:53.500 --> 01:04:56.500
其中一名学生是校报记者
McGhee, who happens to be a reporter for the campus paper,

01:04:56.600 --> 01:04:58.300
他用手机拍下这些画面
captured this on his cell phone.

01:04:58.400 --> 01:05:00.100
国家森林下起一阵雷暴雨
Further search for the mysterious "hulk"

01:05:00.200 --> 01:05:04.700
神秘绿巨人的搜寻行动因此拖延
was postponed by powerful thunderstorms in the Smoky Mountain National Forest.

01:05:05.300 --> 01:05:08.100
"汽车旅馆"

01:05:12.200 --> 01:05:15.200
后面不要剪太短
Not too short back there.

01:05:15.300 --> 01:05:17.700
我以前帮你剪过头发
I have done this before, you know.

01:05:33.600 --> 01:05:36.200
我不知道你自己是怎么剪的
I don't know how you've done this on your own for all this time.

01:05:36.300 --> 01:05:38.200
通常都是用电剪
With clippers, usually.

01:06:33.100 --> 01:06:35.700
等一下
- Wait, wait, wait. Wait. - What? What?

01:06:35.900 --> 01:06:37.200
我们不能这样
We can't do this.

01:06:37.300 --> 01:06:39.400
- 没关系 我想要 - 不
- It's okay. I want to. - No.

01:06:40.500 --> 01:06:41.500
不
No.

01:06:42.700 --> 01:06:43.900
我不行
I can't.

01:06:47.500 --> 01:06:49.500
我不能太兴奋
I can't get too excited.

01:06:52.200 --> 01:06:54.300
一点点都不行吗?
Not even a little excited?

01:06:57.000 --> 01:06:58.400
没关系
It's okay.

01:07:03.000 --> 01:07:04.900
长官 是布朗斯基
Sir, it's Blonsky.

01:07:07.400 --> 01:07:10.300
他有没有家人?
Has anyone found out if he has next of kin or family?

01:07:11.100 --> 01:07:12.700
你自己问他
Ask him yourself.

01:07:16.600 --> 01:07:17.600
长官?
Sir?

01:07:37.800 --> 01:07:41.800
- 很高兴看到你复原 大兵 - 谢谢你 长官
- Good to see you back on your feet, soldier. - Thank you, sir.

01:07:48.800 --> 01:07:50.000
你觉得怎样?
How do you feel?

01:07:52.000 --> 01:07:54.400
超不爽的 我要打第三回合
Pissed off and ready for round three.

01:08:00.900 --> 01:08:04.800
这些都不能用 会被追踪
Basically, we can't use any of this, because they can track all of it.

01:08:05.000 --> 01:08:07.700
我的唇蜜都会被追踪?
