Well, we'll have to try and get it back.

01:08:43.600 --> 01:08:47.500
调查局在监视手机信用卡
Federal is already monitoring phones,plastic and Dr Ross's web accounts,

01:08:47.900 --> 01:08:50.100
和罗博士的纲路帐号
and local PD have been placed on alert.

01:08:50.300 --> 01:08:52.900
当地警方设下临检站 只要他们出现就会通知我们
They'll pop up somewhere and when they do, it comes straight to us.

01:08:53.000 --> 01:08:54.900
他们不会就这样出现
They're not gonna just pop up.

01:08:55.100 --> 01:08:58.100
他这五年来一直在各国游走
He made it five years and got across borders without making any mistakes.

01:08:58.200 --> 01:09:00.000
绝对不会使用信用卡
He's not gonna use a damn credit card now.

01:09:00.400 --> 01:09:02.100
他想逃早就走远了
If he was trying to escape, he'd be long gone.

01:09:02.300 --> 01:09:03.400
这次他不准备逃跑了
He's not trying to escape this time.

01:09:03.500 --> 01:09:06.000
如果他想找人帮忙我们就能逮到他
He's looking for help and that's how we're gonna get him.

01:09:06.100 --> 01:09:08.500
他有和别人联络
We know what they're after and we know he's been talking to somebody.

01:09:08.600 --> 01:09:10.400
你们都看过资料
You all have copies of the correspondence.

01:09:10.900 --> 01:09:12.900
绿先生和蓝先生的昵称
The aliases Mr Green and Mr Blue

01:09:13.100 --> 01:09:16.100
已经加入神盾资料库 标题:绿先生来信
have been added to the SHIELD Operations Database.

01:09:16.200 --> 01:09:17.900
蓝先生 资料在这里 该见面了 绿先生
If he comes up for air, we'll be waiting.

01:09:19.200 --> 01:09:21.300
他一现身 我们马上知道
If he makes a peep, we'll hear him.

01:09:21.500 --> 01:09:23.800
他一出错 我们就会出动
And when he slips up, we'll be ready.

01:09:29.800 --> 01:09:30.800
神盾局

01:09:30.900 --> 01:09:32.000
后勤部

01:09:39.600 --> 01:09:41.600
