山缪史登博士 纽约

01:09:59.100 --> 01:10:00.600
格邦学院

01:10:03.800 --> 01:10:05.500
出售

01:10:09.700 --> 01:10:10.900
笑一个
Smile.

01:10:21.300 --> 01:10:23.000
那是什么感觉?
What is it like?

01:10:24.900 --> 01:10:27.600
变身的感觉是什么?
When it happens, what do you experience?

01:10:28.400 --> 01:10:31.000
记得我们在哈佛自愿参与的
Remember those experiments we volunteered for at Harvard?

01:10:31.100 --> 01:10:33.100
引导幻觉实验吗?
Those induced hallucinations?

01:10:33.900 --> 01:10:37.300
就像那样 再放大一千倍
It's a lot like that, just a thousand times amplified.

01:10:39.200 --> 01:10:43.100
就像把一公升迷幻药倒进我脑袋
It's like someone's poured a litre of acid into my brain.

01:10:43.200 --> 01:10:48.000
- 你记得什么吗? - 只有零星的画面

01:10:48.500 --> 01:10:51.700
太多噪音 我什么也分不清楚
There's too much noise. I can never derive anything out of it.

01:10:51.800 --> 01:10:55.300
- 那么你还是在它里面 - 并没有
- But then it's still you inside it. - No. No, it's not.

01:10:57.800 --> 01:11:01.800
我不晓得 但它在山洞 我觉得它就像知道我一样
I don't know. In the cave, I really felt like it knew me.

01:11:02.700 --> 01:11:04.100
也许你的大脑超载
Maybe your mind is in there,

01:11:04.200 --> 01:11:06.800
失去控制
it's just overcharged and can't process what's happening.

01:11:06.900 --> 01:11:10.200
我不想控制它 我想消灭它
I don't want to control it. I want to get rid of it.

01:11:23.500 --> 01:11:24.900
准备好了吗?
Are you ready?

01:11:25.000 --> 01:11:26.700
这样才旗鼓相当
Let's even the playing field a little.

01:11:30.200 --> 01:11:31.400
开始了
Gentlemen.

01:11:35.400 --> 01:11:39.000
布鲁斯 醒醒 情况不妙
Bruce, wake up. There's something going on.

01:11:42.900 --> 01:11:44.500
前有路障

01:11:44.500 --> 01:11:46.500
准备停车

01:11:50.200 --> 01:11:53.200
我们得下车 慢慢往后面走
We got to go. Walk toward the back. Just don't move too fast.

01:12:08.700 --> 01:12:10.300
好了 来吧
All right. Come.

01:12:24.100 --> 01:12:28.400
到上城很远 坐地铁应该最快
It is a long way uptown. I think the subway's probably quickest.

01:12:29.300 --> 01:12:31.200
我和几百个人挤在车厢
Me in a metal tube, deep underground,

01:12:31.400 --> 01:12:33.800
肯定会被逼到抓狂
with hundreds of people in the most aggressive city in the world?

01:12:33.900 --> 01:12:36.600
没错 咱们坐计程车
Right. Let's get a cab.

01:12:36.600 --> 01:12:40.900
拜托!快点!你开车像个娘儿们!
Come on, now! Let's go! You're too slow! You drive like a woman!

01:12:45.800 --> 01:12:47.300
看到没?一个大美女
- Very nice. You see her? - Oh, my.

01:12:47.500 --> 01:12:50.500
你有没有长眼睛呀?
Very pretty. Watch out, you goat!

01:12:50.700 --> 01:12:52.700
呼吸 呼吸
Breathe, breathe, breathe.

01:12:56.000 --> 01:12:58.700
你疯了吗?
Are you out of your mind?

01:12:58.800 --> 01:13:00.000
怎么?
- What is wrong with you? - What's the matter, baby?

01:13:00.200 --> 01:13:01.800
你不喜欢飙车?
You don't like a good ride?

01:13:03.700 --> 01:13:04.900
大混球
Asshole!

01:13:08.100 --> 01:13:10.600
我可以教你怎么控制怒气
You know, I know a few techniques could help you

01:13:10.700 --> 01:13:14.700
闭嘴 走吧
- manage that anger very effectively. - You zip it. We're walking.

01:13:23.900 --> 01:13:25.800
对不起 史登博士?
Excuse me. Dr Sterns?

01:13:25.900 --> 01:13:28.500
我是伊莉莎白罗斯
- Yes. - I'm sorry to bother you. I'm Elizabeth Ross.

01:13:29.400 --> 01:13:31.400
罗斯博士!
Oh! Dr Ross!

01:13:31.500 --> 01:13:34.400
- 有人想要见你 - 好
- I have someone who'd like to meet you. - Okay.

01:13:36.900 --> 01:13:38.300
蓝先生?
It's Mr Blue, isn't it?

01:13:40.200 --> 01:13:41.600
绿先生?
Mr Green?

01:13:43.800 --> 01:13:47.500
我一直在猜你是不是真有其人
I got to tell you, I've been wondering if you were even real.

01:13:47.600 --> 01:13:49.300
如果是 你长什么样子
And if you were, what would it look like?

01:13:49.400 --> 01:13:54.100
一个蕴藏着这么强大力量的人
A person with that much power lurking in him.

01:13:54.200 --> 01:13:55.800
竟然像你这么不起眼
Nothing could have surprised me more

01:13:55.900 --> 01:13:58.700
让我大吃一惊
than this unassuming man shaking my hand.

01:13:58.900 --> 01:14:01.500
这并不简单...
But, look. We're not strolling into the park for a picnic, here.

01:14:01.600 --> 01:14:03.200
就算一切都顺利
Even if everything goes perfectly,

01:14:03.400 --> 01:14:07.200
引导你变身后注射正确剂量
if we induce an episode, if we get the dosage exactly right,

01:14:08.200 --> 01:14:10.100
你会永远被治愈...
is that going to be a lasting cure

01:14:10.200 --> 01:14:13.500
...或者只是暂时被压制而已?
or just some antidote to suppress that specific flare- up?

01:14:15.800 --> 01:14:17.300
我也不知道
I don't know.

01:14:18.000 --> 01:14:22.700
要是注射的剂量稍微多一点
What I'm saying is that if we overshoot this by even the smallest integer

01:14:23.700 --> 01:14:28.600
就会出现高成份的毒性
we're dealing with concentrations with extraordinary levels of toxicity.

01:14:28.700 --> 01:14:33.200
- 可能会害死他 - 当然了 我敢肯定
- You mean it could kill him. - Kill him? Yeah. I should say so.

01:14:34.900 --> 01:14:37.000
也可能完全相反
You should know that there's a flip side to this, too.

01:14:37.100 --> 01:14:40.600
要是剂量太少 无法压制我
If we miss on the low side, if we induce me and it fails,

01:14:40.800 --> 01:14:43.200
你就会陷入危险
this will be very dangerous for you.

01:14:45.000 --> 01:14:49.000
我一向都是个好奇宝宝
Look. I've always been more curious than cautious,

01:14:49.200 --> 01:14:53.200
从来没出过事 到底要不要做呀?
and that's served me pretty well. So, are we going to do this?

01:15:48.500 --> 01:15:50.100
你有什么感觉?
How you feeling, man?

01:15:51.800 --> 01:15:53.400
像个怪物
Like a monster.

01:16:13.300 --> 01:16:15.000
好了 躺上去
Okay. On the table.

01:16:15.800 --> 01:16:21.200
万一你有强烈反应 这能保护你自己
These will protect you from yourself if you have a strong reaction.

01:16:22.500 --> 01:16:25.400
等你觉得太强烈再告诉我
You can tell me later if you thought it was strong.

01:16:29.600 --> 01:16:34.000
拜托 那些蠢研究生
Oh, come on! Stupid graduate students.

01:16:40.400 --> 01:16:41.900
你 你 你
You, you, you.

01:16:43.500 --> 01:16:46.900
这会是很新奇的感觉
This will be a somewhat novel sensation.

01:16:49.600 --> 01:16:51.100
我们开始了
We have begun.

01:16:52.900 --> 01:16:55.900
血液析离器会混和解药和你的血液
The dialysis machine will mix the antidote with your blood.

01:16:56.100 --> 01:17:00.500
但你要完全变身解药才会起作用
Except the antidote will only take hold once we've achieved a full reaction.

01:17:00.600 --> 01:17:01.700
放轻松
Just relax.

01:17:02.500 --> 01:17:05.800
好了 作业完成
Okay. We are comprehensive.

01:17:09.100 --> 01:17:10.500
拿去
Here you go.

01:17:20.600 --> 01:17:22.500
好了 准备好了吗?
All right. We set to pop?

01:17:25.100 --> 01:17:27.200
你最好别碰他
I'd take your hands off him.

01:17:47.000 --> 01:17:49.000
我的老天!
Oh, my God!

01:18:03.200 --> 01:18:05.200
等等 还没结束
Wait, wait! There's more! Wait!

01:18:16.000 --> 01:18:18.600
- 现在 现在! - 等一下
- Now. Okay, now! - Wait.

01:18:18.700 --> 01:18:21.200
快点!快点!
Now, do it! Do it!

01:18:28.800 --> 01:18:31.300
布鲁斯 看着我
Bruce! Bruce, look at me.

01:18:31.400 --> 01:18:35.800
快注射解药 史登 快呀!
Stay with me. The antidote, now! Sterns, do it now!

01:18:37.300 --> 01:18:41.300
布鲁斯 看着我的眼睛
Bruce, look at me. Look in my eyes. Please, look in my eyes.

01:18:41.400 --> 01:18:44.900
这一定是开玩笑
Oh, you've got to be kidding me!

01:19:04.600 --> 01:19:05.700
布鲁斯
Bruce.

01:19:05.900 --> 01:19:07.200
我的天啊
Oh, my God.

01:19:18.600 --> 01:19:21.600
布鲁斯?你听得见吗?
Bruce? Bruce, can you hear me?

01:19:25.700 --> 01:19:26.800
布鲁斯?
Bruce?

01:19:35.700 --> 01:19:39.000
没事了 你没事了
It's okay. You're okay. You're okay.

01:19:42.500 --> 01:19:43.900
你撑过去了
You did it.

01:19:44.000 --> 01:19:46.700
他没事 太棒了
He's fine. This is fantastic.

01:19:46.800 --> 01:19:48.100
结束了
It's over.

01:19:59.900 --> 01:20:05.800
那是我这辈子见过最惊人的事
That was the most extraordinary thing I have seen in my entire life!

01:20:06.000 --> 01:20:07.500
别这么兴奋
Okay, you know what? Stop, please.

01:20:07.600 --> 01:20:10.000
我们得讨论刚才发生的事
We need to go back and talk about what just happened in there.

01:20:10.100 --> 01:20:13.900
没问题 伽玛脉冲来自大脑的杏仁核
Absolutely. Okay. The gamma pulse came from the amygdala.

01:20:14.000 --> 01:20:15.700
- 我想是罗斯博士的核酸链 - 你还好吗?
- I think Dr Ross's primer...- Are you okay?

01:20:15.800 --> 01:20:19.000
核酸链让你的细胞暂时吸收能量 过一阵子能量就减退
...lets the cells absorb the energy temporarily, and then it abates.

01:20:19.200 --> 01:20:21.900
所以你多年前才没死于辐射病
That's why you didn't die of radiation sickness years ago!

01:20:22.000 --> 01:20:24.700
我们也许中和了这些细胞
Now, maybe we've neutralised those cells permanently,

01:20:24.800 --> 01:20:26.700
或者只是压制这次变身
or maybe we just suppressed that event.

01:20:26.800 --> 01:20:29.100
我猜是后者吧 但是我不确定
I'm inclined to think the latter, but it's hard to know

01:20:29.200 --> 01:20:31.000
我的实验样本从来没有存活
because none of our test subjects ever survived.

01:20:31.100 --> 01:20:32.600
- 当然 他们没有得到核酸链 - 等等
- Of course, they weren't getting the primer! - Wait, wait.

01:20:32.600 --> 01:20:34.100
- 慢着, 你说什么? - 它们没有吸收
- Wait, what did you just say?- They weren't getting

01:20:34.300 --> 01:20:37.000
- 核酸链 - 不 不 实验样本?
- the myostatin primer...- No, no, no. Test subjects?

01:20:37.900 --> 01:20:39.600
什么实验样本?
What test subjects?

01:20:40.400 --> 01:20:41.400
跟我来
Come with me.

01:20:58.500 --> 01:21:02.400
- 布署得如何? - 狙击手负责A区
- What's the activity level? - Snipers are covering Alpha sector.

01:21:03.300 --> 01:21:04.700
我们先用白老鼠做实验
We started on rats and mice,

01:21:04.800 --> 01:21:07.300
但是都死掉 于是得用大型动物
but it just completely fried them, so we had to go bigger.

01:21:07.600 --> 01:21:10.700
我不确定是伽玛或是你的血比较毒
And we still don't know which is more toxic, the gamma or your blood.

01:21:10.800 --> 01:21:14.500
- 什么意思? - 这全都是你的血
- What do you mean, my blood? - Bruce, this is all you.

01:21:15.400 --> 01:21:19.400
你寄给我的并不多 于是我浓缩以后又制造更多
You didn't send me much to work with, so I had to concentrate it and make more.

01:21:19.500 --> 01:21:22.700
只要继续研究就有无限的可能
With a little more trial and error, there's no end to what we can do!

01:21:22.800 --> 01:21:26.500
无穷的潜力
This is potentially Olympian!

01:21:26.600 --> 01:21:30.100
这种伽玛科技有数不尽的用途
This gamma technology has limitless applications.

01:21:30.200 --> 01:21:32.200
我们能发现数百种解药
We'll unlock hundreds of cures.

01:21:32.400 --> 01:21:35.400
让人类对各种疾病完全免疫
We will make humans impervious to disease!

01:21:49.700 --> 01:21:51.300
不 我们得销毁它
No, no, we've got to destroy it.

01:21:51.800 --> 01:21:53.600
- 什么?- 所有
- Wait, what? - All of it.

01:21:53.800 --> 01:21:55.200
今晚就得把这一切烧毁
Tonight. We're gonna incinerate it.

01:21:55.200 --> 01:21:57.500
- 这里的所有? - 什么
- Is this the whole supply? - What...

01:21:57.600 --> 01:21:59.100
我们可以得到诺贝尔奖耶!
We could get the Nobel for this!

01:21:59.200 --> 01:22:01.400
你不知道这东西的力量
You don't understand the power of this thing.

01:22:01.500 --> 01:22:04.100
太危险了 无法控制
It is too dangerous. It cannot be controlled.

01:22:04.800 --> 01:22:06.300
看到目标就开枪
At your discretion, shooter.

01:22:06.400 --> 01:22:07.800
我们三个!这是普罗米修斯的圣火!
three of us!This is Promethean fire!

01:22:07.900 --> 01:22:08.900
仅仅
It's just...

01:22:09.100 --> 01:22:10.300
瞄不准
No shot.

01:22:13.600 --> 01:22:15.400
布朗斯基进去了
Blonsky's going in.

01:22:17.600 --> 01:22:20.500
不准进去 我女儿在里头
Blonsky, stand down. My daughter's in there!

01:22:23.100 --> 01:22:24.200
我们有解药
We have the antidote now.

01:22:24.300 --> 01:22:27.100
他们只想把它当成武器
They don't want the antidote! They want to make it a weapon!

01:22:34.000 --> 01:22:36.000
如果它被政府抢走就完了
And if we let it go, we will never get it back.

01:22:36.200 --> 01:22:38.200
你不知道它的力量有多强大
You don't know how powerful this thing is.

01:22:38.300 --> 01:22:40.300
我也讨厌政府
I hate the government just as much as anyone,

01:22:40.400 --> 01:22:42.200
不过你也未免太紧张了
but you're being a little paranoid, don't you think?

01:22:50.000 --> 01:22:51.500
布鲁斯!布鲁斯!
Bruce! Bruce!

01:22:53.200 --> 01:22:54.400
快走
Get out.

01:22:57.700 --> 01:23:00.500
它在哪里?
Where is it? Come on, where is it?

01:23:04.700 --> 01:23:06.300
让它现身
Show him to me.

01:23:07.900 --> 01:23:09.100
布朗斯基!
Blonsky!

01:23:17.600 --> 01:23:18.700
小姐
Miss!

01:23:20.200 --> 01:23:21.600
披着吧
Take this.

01:23:25.200 --> 01:23:29.800
你敢消灭浩克就得一辈子坐牢
If you took it from me, I'm gonna put you in a hole for the rest of your life.

01:23:35.600 --> 01:23:36.700
贝蒂
Betty.

01:23:38.700 --> 01:23:41.600
我永远不会原谅你这么对他
I will never forgive what you've done to him.

01:23:41.800 --> 01:23:43.100
他是个逃犯
He's a fugitive.

01:23:43.200 --> 01:23:45.100
是你逼他成为逃犯
You made him a fugitive

01:23:45.200 --> 01:23:48.700
为了掩饰你的失败和保护你自己
to cover your failures and to protect your career.

