01:24:34.300 --> 01:24:37.000
不是你做的事 是你要做的事
It's not what you've done. It's what you're gonna do.

01:24:38.000 --> 01:24:40.400
我要你从班纳身上提炼的东西
I want what you got out of Banner. I want that.

01:24:43.900 --> 01:24:47.900
看来你已经注射了一些东西
You look like you've got a little something in you already, don't you?

01:24:49.300 --> 01:24:52.900
我要更多 你也看到他变成浩克
I want more. You've seen what he becomes, right?

01:24:53.600 --> 01:24:54.800
没错
I have.

01:24:55.800 --> 01:24:57.300
它太美了
And it's beautiful.

01:24:58.200 --> 01:24:59.400
就像神一样
Godlike.

01:24:59.600 --> 01:25:01.300
我也要变成那样
Well, I want that.

01:25:03.500 --> 01:25:05.600
你要把我变成那样
I need that. Make me that.

01:25:06.500 --> 01:25:09.400
我不知道你体内有什么
I don't know what you've got inside you already.

01:25:09.600 --> 01:25:11.100
混在一起可能变成
The mix could be

01:25:11.800 --> 01:25:13.300
一个大祸害
an abomination.

01:25:17.000 --> 01:25:19.800
我没说我不愿意
I didn't say I was unwilling.

01:25:20.400 --> 01:25:24.100
我只是需要你的同意
I just need informed consent.

01:25:26.600 --> 01:25:28.400
你也同意了
And you've given it.

01:25:57.300 --> 01:26:00.000
"绿先生-效力14.56%"

01:26:09.500 --> 01:26:13.800
这就是我想跟你解释的事
This is what I was trying to explain.

01:26:13.900 --> 01:26:18.800
我不知道你注射了什么东西
I don't know what you've been ladling into yourself.

01:26:18.900 --> 01:26:20.900
但是很明显起了效用
But clearly it worked.

01:26:21.100 --> 01:26:24.600
我假设你完全听不懂我的话
Let's assume you don't understand a word I'm saying,

01:26:24.800 --> 01:26:29.600
不过还是请你躺回去
but if you'll just get back on the table,

01:26:29.700 --> 01:26:32.200
好让我把你治好
I can fix this.

