- 开枪! - 嘿
Shoot it! - Hey!

01:26:49.600 --> 01:26:50.600
不
No!

01:27:00.300 --> 01:27:02.300
D4呼叫队长
Delta 4 to Leader.

01:27:02.400 --> 01:27:04.100
他们杀死我们两名弟兄
They took out two of our guys, two of our guys!

01:27:04.200 --> 01:27:06.900
布朗斯基和中校还在里头
Blonsky and the Major are still inside!

01:27:09.800 --> 01:27:12.100
快点!快走!
Come on! Move, move, move, move!

01:27:20.100 --> 01:27:21.600
它在那里!
It's over there!

01:27:23.500 --> 01:27:24.600
离开他们
Drop them!

01:27:24.700 --> 01:27:26.900
- 那是什么东西? - 向它开枪!
What is that thing? - Shoot it!

01:27:36.400 --> 01:27:40.200
你开车!快!快走!
Okay. All right! You... You, drive! Let's go! Move, move!

01:27:40.300 --> 01:27:41.600
队长
Delta 4 to Leader! - Go, go, go, go, go!

01:27:41.700 --> 01:27:43.600
有个大怪物从这里逃走
Something big just went off down here!

01:27:44.200 --> 01:27:46.300
将军 你最好听听看
General, you should hear this!

01:27:46.400 --> 01:27:49.300
浩克在街上!重复 浩克在街上!
The Hulk is in the street! I repeat, the Hulk is in the street!

01:27:51.900 --> 01:27:53.900
不可能 先冷静下来
That's impossible. You get a hold of yourself, young man.

01:27:54.100 --> 01:27:55.900
你在哪里?
You get it together. What is your position?

01:27:56.200 --> 01:27:59.300
121街和北向百老汇路口
121st Street, heading north on Broadway!

01:27:59.400 --> 01:28:01.000
快掉头
Turn us around.

01:28:08.000 --> 01:28:11.100
我们为什么要回去?
We're going back. Why are we going back?

01:28:11.200 --> 01:28:12.800
给我影像
Damn it! Give me eyes down there!

01:28:13.300 --> 01:28:14.500
是 长官
Yes, sir!

01:28:16.600 --> 01:28:18.500
那是什么东西?
What the hell was that?

01:28:18.800 --> 01:28:20.400
快 快
Go, go, go!

01:28:44.000 --> 01:28:45.200
不!
No!

01:29:01.500 --> 01:29:02.800
你的实验品吗?
One of yours?

01:29:03.100 --> 01:29:06.200
天啊 你做了什么?
Oh, my God. What have you done?

01:29:08.600 --> 01:29:10.400
开火!开火!
Fire at him, fire at him!

01:29:14.700 --> 01:29:16.800
你想它怕子弹吗?
Do you think a rifle's gonna hurt that?

01:29:17.200 --> 01:29:18.400
走吧!
Come on!

01:29:22.000 --> 01:29:23.100
水喔
Sweet.

01:29:45.300 --> 01:29:46.600
赶快撤退!
Get out of there, soldier!

01:30:22.300 --> 01:30:24.100
给我更强的对手
Give me a real fight!

01:30:32.300 --> 01:30:33.400
长官?
Sir?

01:30:36.100 --> 01:30:37.200
长官?
Sir?

01:30:38.800 --> 01:30:41.700
下令把所有军力调到哈林区
Tell them to bring everything they've got and head for Harlem.

01:30:45.200 --> 01:30:48.600
让我去 你一定要让我去
It has to be me. You have to take me back there.

01:30:48.900 --> 01:30:50.500
你在说什么?
What are you saying?

01:30:50.700 --> 01:30:51.900
你以为你能控制它?
You think you can control it?

01:30:52.000 --> 01:30:55.100
不是控制 而是利用它
No, no, not control it, but, I don't know, maybe aim it.

01:30:55.200 --> 01:30:56.700
要是不行呢?
And what if you can't?

01:30:58.200 --> 01:31:00.000
这东西是我们创造出来的
We made this thing.

01:31:00.500 --> 01:31:01.800
我们所有人
All of us.

01:31:02.800 --> 01:31:04.000
求求你
Please.

01:31:09.000 --> 01:31:11.500
- 降落在它附近 - 不 留在高空
- Land us near it. - No, no. No, keep us high.

01:31:13.100 --> 01:31:14.400
打开后舱门
Open the back door.

01:31:20.200 --> 01:31:25.000
布鲁斯 站住 你在做什么?
Bruce! Bruce, stop! Stop! What are you doing?

01:31:25.200 --> 01:31:28.800
你要想清楚 你不知道自己会不会变身
Think about this! You don't even know if you'll change!

01:31:30.900 --> 01:31:34.000
别这么做 太疯狂了
You don't have to do this! Please, this is insane!

01:31:34.200 --> 01:31:35.900
贝蒂 我得试一试
Betty, I've got to try.

01:31:38.100 --> 01:31:39.400
对不起
I'm sorry.

01:32:07.700 --> 01:32:10.500
- 把她拉进来 - 来吧 小姐
- Get her in here! - Come on, miss.

01:32:28.000 --> 01:32:30.000
贝蒂 它在那里
There. Betty!

01:32:49.100 --> 01:32:50.700
浩克!
Hulk!

01:32:55.500 --> 01:32:57.100
太好了!
Yeah!

01:33:41.400 --> 01:33:42.600
来吧!
Come on!

01:34:14.900 --> 01:34:16.800
你只有这点料吗?
Is that all you've got?

01:34:30.600 --> 01:34:33.300
快用机关枪!帮助他!
Use that thing, soldier! Give him some help!

01:34:33.500 --> 01:34:34.700
帮哪一个?
Which one?

01:34:34.800 --> 01:34:37.100
绿色的那一个
Help the green one, damn it! Which one do you think?

01:34:37.200 --> 01:34:39.000
把另一个射死
Cut the other one in half!

01:34:41.700 --> 01:34:42.800
罗斯!
Ross!

01:35:07.700 --> 01:35:09.400
继续开火!
Keep it on him!

01:35:37.600 --> 01:35:40.600
- 我得紧急迫降 - 抓紧了!
Look, I got to put it down! - Hang on!

01:36:47.800 --> 01:36:48.900
爸?
Dad?

01:36:51.600 --> 01:36:54.100
你没事吧?我来帮你
Are you hurt? Let me help you.

01:37:01.900 --> 01:37:03.700
我没事 快想办法出去
I'm all right. Just find a way out.

01:37:51.600 --> 01:37:58.200
你不配拥有这种力量 眼睁睁看她死吧!
You don't deserve this power! Now watch her die!

01:38:49.000 --> 01:38:50.600
小心!
Look out!

01:39:21.500 --> 01:39:22.700
将军?
General?

01:39:29.000 --> 01:39:31.500
你有遗言吗?
Any last words?

01:39:34.300 --> 01:39:37.700
浩克出击!
Hulk smash!

01:40:25.300 --> 01:40:26.900
住手!
Stop!

01:41:47.600 --> 01:41:48.900
没事了
It's okay.

01:41:59.100 --> 01:42:00.700
贝蒂
Betty.

