我早就告诉过你了
You know, I hate to say, "I told you so," General,

01:45:00.000 --> 01:45:04.400
超级大兵计划被终止不是没原因
but that Super Soldier programme was put on ice for a reason.

01:45:04.500 --> 01:45:07.300
我一向觉得硬体比较可靠
I've always felt hardware was more reliable.

01:45:07.600 --> 01:45:09.900
- 史塔克 - 将军
- Stark. - General.

01:45:12.200 --> 01:45:14.700
你总是穿得光鲜亮丽
You always wear such nice suits.

01:45:15.700 --> 01:45:17.000
说得好
Touch?

01:45:17.900 --> 01:45:21.600
- 听说你有个不寻常的问题 - 你不用说我也知道
- I hear you have an unusual problem. - You should talk.

01:45:21.700 --> 01:45:23.200
听我说
You should listen.

01:45:25.900 --> 01:45:28.700
我们正在组织一个联盟
What if I told you we were putting a team together?

01:45:29.500 --> 01:45:31.000
"我们"是谁?
Who's "we"?
